@KashGetCarter @RTFKTstudios I guess it's how you view RTFKT. I wouldn't call it an add on. Both clonex and mnlth are part of a much greater ecosystem, along with pods, wearables and whatever else they imagine up.

@missmerghu @RTFKTstudios Yes. Great analogy. I had no idea that final fantasy would turn into an epic franchise when I played the original back on NES. But I knew I definitely wanted more of that aweso formula. The same is playing out here in the mv.
@missmerghu @RTFKTstudios Yes it's true. The hype is real someone once said. I'm glad we found something we can sustain enthusiasm about over the long run.

@CryptoTron72 @RTFKTstudios Yea thats for sure. If you approach it like "I'm going to make 200x over 12 months" it sounds a lot better than trying to make a 2-3x in a week. Where do you think we will be in 12 months from now?
